Sleep 3s
Hide
Type " "
Backspace
Show
Sleep 3s
Hide
Type " "
Backspace
Show
Sleep 3s
Hide
Type " "
Backspace
Show
Sleep 1s

# Prompt 2
Type "@samples/book-app-project/books.py What code handles the search functionality?"
Sleep 2s
Enter

# Wait for response (with periodic nudges to keep input visible)
